{"tid":621592,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺升左U之後仲問老豆老母拎錢D人好廢柴","createTime":"2018-04-08T12:31:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-08T13:03:25.000Z","uid":68626,"like":4,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7c5fde785e38619a05bc59e8e64c2745c22cc157","tid":621592,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T12:31:20.000Z","msg":"咁大個人 番學番得三/四日<br />\n咁多日子得閒 仲唔番工 問老豆老母拎錢個D係咪廢柴黎<br />\n樓下應該有D傻西係到覆咩 老豆大把錢 每月30K零用是否廢柴?<br />\n我答你<br />\n係呀 你係廢柴呀 你係一個無老豆老母就無撚用既廢柴<br />\n利申 當年自從上左YEAR3之後無問老豆老母拎過錢<br />\n但佢地仲成日偷放錢係我銀包到 好侮辱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edac9a8d2a2a0a13a68b1d51f7bd7e8aeb643e85","tid":621592,"uid":50779,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T12:32:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"714aadf027ecd8ef9362bc2c8d6f1320c0fa16a6","tid":621592,"uid":118623,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T12:33:39.000Z","msg":"Your opinion does not matter 🤷🏿&zwj;♂️"},{"pid":"4ee79b4a2312e1556de126fbd9e32dcb22ca16f7","tid":621592,"uid":4526,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T12:36:21.000Z","msg":"好彩我係問政府拎錢姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"172767b5eb9655c46fb32cc9a9de7f747f1fafeb","tid":621592,"uid":136038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T12:37:30.000Z","msg":"想做廢柴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fba22f75f3be300d2c8ba2919f13c98ca89a7942","tid":621592,"uid":180913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T12:38:13.000Z","msg":"我情緒問題無野做個時都係咁做<br />\n好無用<br />\n好在屋企環境都ok<br />\n支持到我情緒問題俾我摺左成年"},{"pid":"dbfefb7a5ff49553655e4ce1e21003793399b88e","tid":621592,"uid":180913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T12:39:07.000Z","msg":"有能力邊個想洗人錢啊<br />\n洗錢個位都好無安全感<br />\n日日想死咁"},{"pid":"d